      "id": "1087907357729915",
      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Best version of clouds yet",
      "review_description": "This has to be the best version\nFirst off, most of the maps are kind of like the OG versions for example beach. beach is the blackout days ￼\n\nAnd what I also like about this game are the abilities￼\n\nAnd I love how city is like a game mode hub where all of the maps are organized\n\nAlso, I’m going to tell a few steps or whatever to you guys (not the devs the players)\n\nFirst off if you spawn in chimp, lab uninstall the game and reinstall it \n\nSecond off  if you want the game to become less laggy, go to settings \n\nThird off if you were having troubles connecting to lobby either wait or wait for clouds to get better CCU \n\nAlso, don’t tell lies in the reviews\nFor example, I saw a kid that lied saying their headset exploded and burned down their house \n\nBut this game is actually good so I’d recommend you download it and play it \n\nAlso Dev’s  keep up the good work ￼￼￼￼￼￼￼￼￼￼",
